<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0007a" xml:id="I01.0003.0007a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0007a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 3</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0007a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>元景造石窟記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0007a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0007a0101">惟大魏太和廿三年歲次己卯四<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">月</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">丙</unclear>午朔八日<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">癸</unclear>丑
<lb ed="I" n="0007a02" type="honorific"/>諸軍事平東將軍營州刺史元景。上為
<lb ed="I" n="0007a03" type="honorific"/>皇帝陛下敬造石窟一區
<lb ed="I" n="0007a04" type="honorific"/>夫靈覺沖虛。非像無以<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0007001" n="0007001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0007001" n="0007001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0007001" n="0007001"/>筌<anchor xml:id="end0007001"/>其形。妙門潛寂。非唱．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a05" type="honorific"/>生滅。昧識於慧旦。將以輪迴塵網。纏服衰弊<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">矣</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a06" type="honorific"/>釋加如來。契慈心於因初。達妙致於遐劫。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">揖</unclear>慧舟以拯溺。夷<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">阻</unclear>濟艱。人天仰德。功蓋．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a08" type="honorific"/>我皇代受命光□□□日新。景福增崇。聖．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a09" type="honorific"/>皇帝陛下。誕<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">稟</unclear>□□□高振古。遊神虛宗。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a10" type="honorific"/>興援及州鎮。靡不□□況景藉蔭洪□根□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a11" type="honorific"/>土雖麗。豈同巖石之固。於州城東北一百．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a12" type="honorific"/>暨浩滄。右帶龍川。臨清流以藻穢。背脩巒．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a13" type="honorific"/>明。可以軌矚。東民信之。威訓穆然。存道久．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a14" type="honorific"/>皇帝陛下。資化無為。一同率土。享祚齊．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a15" type="honorific"/>明元皇帝。栖神常住。降及一切。普沾．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a16" type="honorific"/>是詣。速證大果。又願己身。并諸眷屬。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a17" type="honorific"/>文靡述。國之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0007002" n="0007002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0007002" n="0007002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0007002" n="0007002"/>休<anchor xml:id="end0007002"/>祉。可無稱乎。故於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">石</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a18" type="honorific"/>玄覺體<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">空</unclear>。真□□□公誰究竟。悟茲．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a19" type="honorific"/>空有同照。無<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">微</unclear>□□。調風灑澤。懷．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a20" type="honorific"/>詳陟<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">人</unclear>合。想<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">作</unclear>□□。彫巖鏤<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">飾</unclear>。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a21" type="honorific"/>建茲<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">華</unclear>窟。投心請慶。仰願聖．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0007a22" type="honorific"/>上願明元。神栖妙宮。受道．．．</p>
